title: The Sword God From a Fallen World
description: The Sword God From a Fallen World Manhwa The world has ended. A realm consumed by death and despair. And the man who fought until the very end—the Sword God, Karserian Le Vandein. But as if guided by fate, a door to another world opened. Beyond it lay Earth, still pristine, untouched… The Sword God from a Ruined World, 멸망한 세계에서 온 검신
alternative_titles: The Sword God from a Ruined World
